# Agent Chaos Runbook

## Port-forward nhanh

```bash
kubectl port-forward svc/my-grafana 3000:80 -n monitoring
kubectl port-forward svc/chaos-dashboard 2333:30329 -n chaos-mesh
sudo k3s kubectl port-forward pod/chaos-dashboard-6b9c9c6ff7-95d57 8080:2333 -n chaos-mesh --address 0.0.0.0
sudo k3s kubectl port-forward pod/my-grafana-786d99cb8d-d4lh6 3000:3000 -n monitoring --address 0.0.0.0
sudo kubectl port-forward pod/myapp-7876455b56-scshr 3000:3000 -n backend
```

## Ke hoach chaos 24h

- Runbook chi tiet: `LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-24h-plan.md`
- Huong dan chay: `LAB_CENTER/agent/HUONG_DAN_CHAOS_MESH_VA_PYTHON_METRICS.md`
- Manifest: `LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/`
- Label terms: `LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-labeling-terms.md`
- Label rules YAML: `LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-labeling-rules.yaml`

Chay 24h schedule mode (khong chay chung voi immediate mode):

```bash
kubectl apply -f LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/00-common-labels.yaml
kubectl apply -f LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/01-chaos-target-nginx.yaml
kubectl rollout status deploy/chaos-target-nginx -n backend --timeout=120s
kubectl apply -f LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/30-schedules-24h.yaml
```

Luu y: IOChaos da duoc cau hinh inject tren `/mnt/chaos`, khong inject vao root filesystem `/`.
Khong `kubectl apply -f` ca thu muc vi se tao ca immediate chaos (`10/11/20/21`) va schedule cung luc, de xay ra xung dot tc/ipset.

Xem trang thai:

```bash
kubectl get iochaos,networkchaos,dnschaos,stresschaos,schedules -n backend
```

Cleanup:

```bash
kubectl delete -f LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/
```

## Tao dataset metric + label (30s)

```bash
python LAB_CENTER/agent/main.py \
	--prom-url http://localhost:9090 \
	--start 2026-03-20T00:00:00 \
	--end 2026-03-21T00:00:00 \
	--step 30s \
	--rules LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-labeling-rules.yaml \
	--output LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos_labeled_30s.csv
```
